overview:
Primus Cable - Your Value Leader In Structured Cabling Solutions With decades of cumulative experience in the industry, Primus Cable is a leading supplier of wire, cable, and interconnection products, servicing the electrical, electronic, and communication industries.

At Primus Cable, we are dedicated to providing you with the highest caliber of products possible with exceptional, factory direct savings. Whether your project is big or small, our team is here to assist you meet your needs while helping you stay under budget.

Your Total Installation Solution At Primus Cable, we carry everything you need to get the job done, including: alarm cable, security cable, audio cable, CAT3 cable, CAT5E cable, CAT6 cable, CAT6A cable, coaxial cable, ethernet switches, fiber optic products, home theater products, keystone jacks, modular plugs & boots, patch cords, patch panels & brackets, PC cables, surface mount boxes, telco products, tools, wall plates & inserts, wire & cable management, workstation solutions, and more!
